column7: A skate bike including a frame;

pair of pedals provided on either side of the wheel;
pair of supporting shafts pivotally provided on the
frame at suitable position to define a support for feet of
and an auxiliary wheel set provided on the
frame at a suitable position. The skate bike is effective as
an unicycle and also effective as an ice scooter or a grass
